{"name": "odoo-addon-purchase-return", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-purchase-return", "version": "16.0.1.0.1.1", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Lesser General Public License v3 (LGPLv3)", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/purchase-workflow", "license": "LGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Manage return orders.", "upload_time": 1724213197}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Alpha-red.png\n    :alt: Alpha\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-LGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: LGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fpurchase--workflow-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/purchase-workflow\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/purchase-workflow/tree/16.0/purchase_return\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/purchase-workflow-16-0/purchase-workflow-16-0-purchase_return\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/purchase-workflow&target_branch=16.0\n    ```\n  maintainer-JordiBForgeFlow: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/JordiBForgeFlow.png?size=40px\n    :alt: JordiBForgeFlow\n    :target: https://github.com/JordiBForgeFlow\n    ```\n---\n\n# Purchase Return\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:fe2c32a532313fb86ab16d02dc9f2088ba8a607a1cfbff1fa7a4492691bedfcc\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module allows to create Purchase Return Orders. Typically vendors expect\nto receive Purchase Return Orders as the starting event for claims associated\nwith products or services delivered.\n\nThe process work pretty much the same as with Purchase Orders, but the flow\nis inverted. Upon indication of quantities delivered (representing the\nservices that have been accepted to be refunded for, or products returned) you\ncan create the subsequent refund bills.\n\n:::{IMPORTANT}\nThis is an alpha version, the data model and design can change at any time without warning.\nOnly for development or testing purpose, do not use in production.\n[More details on development status](https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status)\n:::\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use this module, you need to:\n\n- Attribute a type when editing purchase requests\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/purchase-workflow/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/purchase-workflow/issues/new?body=module:%20purchase_return%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- ForgeFlow\n\n### Contributors\n\n- ForgeFlow, S.L.\n\n  > - Jordi Ballester Alomar \\<<mailto:jordi.ballester@forgeflow.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainer](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-JordiBForgeFlow }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/purchase-workflow](https://github.com/OCA/purchase-workflow/tree/16.0/purchase_return) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models.account_move", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models..account_move", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models.account_move_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models..account_move_line", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models.product_category", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models..product_category", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models.product_template", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models..product_template", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models.purchase_return_order", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models..purchase_return_order", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models.purchase_return_order_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models..purchase_return_order_line", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.purchase_return.models.account_move_line", "documentation": ["Copyright 2021 ForgeFlow, S.L. (https://www.forgeflow.com)", "License LGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl)."], "fu